msgctxt "release_note_181"
msgid ""
"18.1:\n"
"-A Weekly Roundup: a summary of activity (views, likes, comments) on your most-used sites, sent to you each Monday.\n"
"-A toggle option in the Embed block to resize embedded content, like videos and other media, on smaller devices.\n"
"-A time selection feature that lets you choose a specific time to receive a Blogging Reminder.\n"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "release_note_180"
msgid ""
"18.0:\n"
"We’ve optimized theme images for faster downloads and a lighter impact on your data plan.\n"
"\n"
"We also added Global Style Colors to Full Site Editing themes, made some behind-the-scenes improvements to the comments experience, and squashed a bug that prevented the ‘More’ toolbar from appearing in the Unsupported Block Editor.\n"
msgstr ""

